ActAeronautics Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Aviation Security Regulations, 2012 (Airport Security Programs)
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION SECURITY REGULATIONS, 2012 (AIRPORT SECURITY PROGRAMS) in order to (1) enhance airport security program requirements; and (2) further revise and clarify certain aspects of the Regulations, including both older, more complex issues and issues raised since publication of the first phase of aviation security program requirements.
